rich_summary.display_description: Get ready to groove with the Booty Scooty Robin, an entertaining figure that dances to its own beat! Perfect for fans of Teen Titans Go, this Robin figure comes equipped with a press-activated dancing feature. Simply press Robin's foot, and watch him break into dance, twerking along to catchy tunes that are sure to bring a smile to anyone's face. A true collectible, Booty Scooty Robin is designed for play and display, making it a striking addition to any Teen Titans Go collection. PRESS TO DANCE: Activate Robin's groovy dance moves by pressing the foot button, bringing this beloved character to life with fun and excitement. Batteries included! CATCHY MUSIC: Includes built-in music that plays when Robin starts to dance! Groove with Robin to the music! WATCH ROBIN TWERK: Watch as Robin's booty twerks up and down in rhythm with the music, making this a standout, amusing toy for any fan. PLAY OR DISPLAY: Perfect for display, this Robin figure makes a great addition to any Teen Titans Go! Collection! Includes: 1 Figure. Size H29cm. Batteries required: 2 x AA (included). EAN: 681147014633. WARNING(S): Only for domestic use.
